snippet: The Dolphins have parted ways with general manager Dennis Hickey after two seasons, the team announced on Saturday, his lavish spending unable to help Miami end a playoff drought that stretches back to 2008....
lead_paragraph: The Dolphins have parted ways with general manager Dennis Hickey after two seasons, the team announced on Saturday, his lavish spending unable to help Miami end a playoff drought that stretches back to 2008.

headline.main: Dophins Ditch GM Hickey After Second Poor Season
headline.print_headline: Dophins Ditch GM Hickey After Second Poor Season
